{"metadata":{"name":"Jami At Tirmidhi","section":{"23":"The Book on Jihad"},"section_detail":{"23":{"hadithnumber_first":1670,"hadithnumber_last":1719,"arabicnumber_first":1670,"arabicnumber_last":1719}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1710,"arabicnumber":1710,"text":"حدثنا احمد بن منيع، حدثنا روح بن عبادة، عن ابن جريج، عن ابي الزبير، عن جابر، ان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم نهى عن الوسم في الوجه والضرب . قال ابو عيسى هذا حديث حسن صحيح","grades":[{"name":"Ahmad Muhammad Shakir","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Bashar Awad Maarouf","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":23,"hadith":43}}]}